trans-unit.source: Creates and maintains the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior" /> sub-element in the service behaviors section of a Sql workflow configuration file.
trans-unit.target: 建立及保留 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior" /> 子項目，這個子項目位於 Sql 工作流程組態檔的服務行為區段。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior> object contains settings to control event tracking behavior in a workflow application.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior> 物件包含了可控制工作流程應用程式中事件追蹤行為的設定。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Configuration.EtwTrackingBehaviorElement" /> 執行個體的型別。

trans-unit.source: The type of an event tracking behavior element.
trans-unit.target: 事件追蹤行為物件項目的型別。

trans-unit.source: Returns a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 傳回 <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Activities.Description.EtwTrackingBehavior" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An instance of an event tracking behavior object.
trans-unit.target: 事件追蹤行為物件的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets the tracking profile name parameter for the event tracking behavior element.
trans-unit.target: 取得事件追蹤行為項目的追蹤設定檔名稱參數。

trans-unit.source: The tracking profile filters for specific event tracking data that the workflow runtime generates.
trans-unit.target: 追蹤設定檔會篩選工作流程執行階段所產生的特定事件追蹤資料。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection" /> of the current event tracking behavior element.
trans-unit.target: 取得目前事件追蹤行為項目的 <see cref="T:System.Configuration.ConfigurationPropertyCollection" />。
